            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chorizo is cooking, add the<strong> flaked almonds</strong> to a baking tray and put in the oven for 3-6 min or until toasted</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
