          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice the<strong> lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into wedges, then peel and roughly chop the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Top, tail and peel the<strong> courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into lengths, until you end up with a pile of courgette ribbons</p><p>Trim and finely slice the<strong> spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>,<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>then<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>crumble the <strong>feta</strong></p><p>Combine the juice of 1/2<strong> </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[1] </span><strong>lemon</strong> with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> lemon dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
