          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>chickpeas</strong> to a <strong>food processor </strong>with the<strong> chopped garlic</strong>, 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and the juice of the <strong>remaining lemon</strong></p><p>Add 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>cooked chorizo</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) and all of the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>chorizo oil</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and blitz until fully combined and smooth – this is your <strong>chorizo hummus</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
