          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained bulgur</strong>,<strong> lemon dressing</strong>, <strong>crumbled feta</strong>, <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong> and <strong>courgette ribbons</strong> to a large bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>feta & courgette salad</strong></p>",
